Andy Murray will marry long-term girlfriend Kim Sears at Dunblane Cathedral next week . 
  The tennis star has said he 'couldn't care less' about the finer details of the wedding . 
  Murray said he was involved in the cake tasting but has left the rest to his fiancee . 
